. 39. The measurement of resistance by Wheatstone bridge is not affected by the internal resistance of the cell. 40. In case of zero deflection in the galvanometer current flows in the primary circuit of the potentiometer, not in the galvanometer circuit. 41. A potentiometer can act as an ideal voltmeter. JEE | NEET | Class 8 - 10 Download eSaral App www.esaral.com Rev. Notes Class 12 Physics Chap